@NODE Preface "1.1  Preface"
@{u}@{b}1.1  Preface@{uu}@{ub}

IntuiCookie is a program that will display fortune cookies.

Some people might say that a MUI fortune cookie program is overkill.
I don't think so.

Just @{"install" LINK Installation} IntuiCookie and draw your own conclusions.


__________
@{i}Pohls' Law:
Nothing is so good that somebody, somewhere, will not hate it.@{ui}
@ENDNODE





@NODE Features "1.2  Why should I use IntuiCookie?"
@{u}@{b}1.2  Why should I use IntuiCookie?@{uu}@{ub}

· IntuiCookie uses a (highly-configurable) MUI window to display the cookie.
· IntuiCookiecan be extensively customised via a Prefs window.
  It offers much more features than any other Amiga fortune cookie program.
· IntuiCookie uses hash files for fast access; a hashfile generator is
  included in the program; the creation of the hashfile can be customised.
· Formatting characters are supported.  Cookies can contain bold, italic
  underlined and highlighted characters in three different alignements.

· ... and much more... ;-)

@ENDNODE





